{"tha-ap434:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap434:0.2":"Ekaviharivagga ","tha-ap434:0.3":"Ekasankhiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap434:1.1":"“Vipassino bhagavato, ","tha-ap434:1.2":"mahabodhimaho ahu; ","tha-ap434:1.3":"Mahajana samagamma, ","tha-ap434:1.4":"pujenti bodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap434:2.1":"Na hi tam orakam manne, ","tha-ap434:2.2":"buddhasettho bhavissati; ","tha-ap434:2.3":"Yassayam idisa bodhi, ","tha-ap434:2.4":"pujaniya ca satthuno. ","tha-ap434:3.1":"Tato sankham gahetvana, ","tha-ap434:3.2":"bodhirukkhamupatthahim; ","tha-ap434:3.3":"Dhamanto sabbadivasam, ","tha-ap434:3.4":"avandim bodhimuttamam. ","tha-ap434:4.1":"Asannake katam kammam, ","tha-ap434:4.2":"devalokam apapayi; ","tha-ap434:4.3":"Kalevaram me patitam, ","tha-ap434:4.4":"devaloke ramamaham. ","tha-ap434:5.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap434:5.2":"tutthahattha pamodita; ","tha-ap434:5.3":"Sada mayham upatthanti, ","tha-ap434:5.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap434:6.1":"Ekasattatime kappe, ","tha-ap434:6.2":"raja asim sudassano; ","tha-ap434:6.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap434:6.4":"jambumandassa issaro. ","tha-ap434:7.1":"Tato angasata turiya, ","tha-ap434:7.2":"parivarenti mam sada; ","tha-ap434:7.3":"Anubhomi sakam kammam, ","tha-ap434:7.4":"upatthanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap434:8.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap434:8.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap434:8.3":"Matukucchigatassapi, ","tha-ap434:8.4":"vajjare bheriyo sada. ","tha-ap434:9.1":"Upatthitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap434:9.2":"anubhutvana sampada; ","tha-ap434:9.3":"Sivam sukhemam amatam, ","tha-ap434:9.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap434:10.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap434:10.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap434:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap434:10.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap434:11.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap434:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap434:11.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap434:12.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap434:12.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap434:12.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap434:13.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap434:13.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap434:13.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap434:14.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekasankhiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap434:15.1":"Ekasankhiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}